  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You create a vine-like whip covered in thorns that lashes out at your command toward a creature in range. Make a melee spell attack against the target. On a hit, the target takes [[/damage 1d6 piercing]] damage, and if it is Large or smaller, you can pull it up to 10 feet closer to you.</p><p><strong>Cantrip Upgrade.</strong> The damage increases by 1d6 when you reach levels 5 ([[/damage 2d6 piercing]]), 11 ([[/damage 3d6 piercing]]), and 17 ([[/damage 4d6 piercing]]).</p>",
